{"tid":1473741,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"呂秉權: 解放軍壓境可有多個不同程度解讀","createTime":"2019-08-15T02:43:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T04:59:28.000Z","uid":7971,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"93a6c1ba28bed868690c61fbc7ae557b3979a06d","tid":1473741,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T02:43:17.000Z","msg":"【重要知識，知己知彼】解放軍壓境可有多個不同程度解讀，由最初階到最嚴重列之：<br />\n<br />\n1）後勤兵源調港：<br />\n解放軍駐港部隊有大約8000-10000多兵力，本身一半駐港，一半留守深圳同樂軍營，中央軍委將原本的深圳後備兵源全數調往香港。<br />\n<br />\n2）在駐軍一萬兵力之上增兵，新兵源包括：<br />\n&mdash; a)中山軍分區（約一萬人，曾在八一「後果自負」演習中以「藍軍」形式意外曝光）；<br />\n&mdash;b)駐地惠州、幅射香港的第74集團軍（6-10萬人，曾在湛江演習亮相）調兵增援駐港部隊；<br />\n&mdash;c)以上增兵可壓境深圳亦可候命調港；<br />\n&mdash;d)當全面補充兵源後，解放軍可有十多萬人對港，是原來的十倍或以上； <br />\n<br />\n3）刻意換防：<br />\n駐港部隊一般每年年底換防一次，再換新血，這次有可能以換防之名高調讓部隊在市區穿梭。<br />\n<br />\n4）駐港部隊低度出動，但能見度高：<br />\n&mdash;在全港約廿處軍事用地內外高調布防和巡邏，其中包括赤鱲角機場軍事運輸中心；<br />\n&mdash;在中央駐港設施（中聯辦、外交部駐港特派員公署、中資機構）等布防；<br />\n&mdash;在象徵國家主權的國旗設施設防（金紫荊廣場、政總等）<br />\n&mdash;在特區政府設施和西九高鐵站等布防。<br />\n<br />\n5）駐軍在市區大量調動兵力、軍車、軍備、新的防暴武器（清障裝甲車 、聲波炮、鎮暴系統等）、甚至彈導導彈（佔中時期，駐港部隊曾於新疆試射），震懾港人；<br />\n<br />\n6）與港警在市區/警校街景進行反暴動演習；<br />\n<br />\n7）駐軍正式出動「平暴」。<br />\n<br />\n/<br />\n<br />\n我屌哂你哋啊<br />\n之前又不知幾想出<br />\n一出又話咩老母wtsapp今朝都收到<br />\n好似好撚驚咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係出 都有唔同程度<br />\n仲要依家都講到明 係出都先出武警<br />\n同老解依家最多 係區內兜下圈做下show"},{"pid":"0684cfc0f98ed4a3fade9c475d0bdb91250aade7","tid":1473741,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T02:43:31.000Z","msg":"自己睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ef5d3f3afdf81a22ad7ef8062eda66b34fecb15","tid":1473741,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T02:49:20.000Z","msg":"睇"},{"pid":"a2e41137035eb84dbefd88546d83a8aabfc7bdb0","tid":1473741,"uid":149361,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T02:54:17.000Z","msg":"驚閪"},{"pid":"f0064c6df78f8fe8654c432322784a94dd051b07","tid":1473741,"uid":264724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T02:55:20.000Z","msg":"求推求推! 超簡單 全民集氣 方法 一定要谷到 全香港支持運動嘅人都識做<br />\n<br />\n全民係屋企都可以示威:<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Noise-Making&nbsp;定時敲鑊抗爭法</span></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1469010\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1469010</a>"},{"pid":"b49129b3a13b8d289507645aaf4ad434d98ba15f","tid":1473741,"uid":46431,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T02:57:21.000Z","msg":"快撚d啦等到天光都未黎<br />\n黎左睇下維狗定我地後生仔大獲d"},{"pid":"216cb4af78008e20b6e0533d5d0f19aa227f9312","tid":1473741,"uid":171992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T02:57:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/6yR8ycR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6yR8ycR.jpg&h=a587efad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg&h=b7bac505&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg&h=42f5c084&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141101_1e69ec3ac35774384c7044962c18e307.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141101_1e69ec3ac35774384c7044962c18e307.png&h=4a3dc024&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141106_a064336a869290c4a85c50e2c5342faf.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141106_a064336a869290c4a85c50e2c5342faf.jpeg&h=42d70b2e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3b2704c5c3e4b3dd058f405743b492651add742b","tid":1473741,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T02:58:39.000Z","msg":"最好放核彈"},{"pid":"77b5cccb7524e44dee9fc16909e1cbd4ac12df64","tid":1473741,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:01:43.000Z","msg":"驚驚驚 <br />\n驚就大家一齊翻屋企"},{"pid":"cee43278cd13591e83e86a0d16f83be1bdf9eee4","tid":1473741,"uid":4964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:03:16.000Z","msg":"快啲出"},{"pid":"bdbbccdf3fb3863f0f43a8cd1ce1e412ae33bf7e","tid":1473741,"uid":304321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:03:22.000Z","msg":"好驚呀 我返屋企訓教先啦"},{"pid":"b4d3731006e5b227406f72408da6a95731894d83","tid":1473741,"uid":115910,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:03:26.000Z","msg":"根本大撚把人真心驚到仆街"},{"pid":"b8191388cae3d04b9e68690a3716cf280e3aaa6e","tid":1473741,"uid":51698,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:03:46.000Z","msg":"咁早就想放風嚇人唔好出黎818<br />\n露晒底<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46b0b17248a97d1abd425ed17244283f358f8103","tid":1473741,"uid":14075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:08:49.000Z","msg":"對內 武警&gt;解放軍"},{"pid":"1fc07ef9177d319f57e73d0a69c6eb0ff8b47792","tid":1473741,"uid":284932,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:11:52.000Z","msg":"有錯請指教 <br />\n<br />\n深圳步隊來港只需10分鐘, 如果老共真係要出動深圳步隊來香港, 深圳步隊未嚟之前, 我諗佢地先會出動駐港步隊癱瘓香港既通訊設施和網絡, 例如電話打唔到呀, 手機無訊號呀, 上唔到網呀, 睇唔到電視呀, 聽唔到收音機呀, 等等, 以防出動老解的消息和新聞傳出去外國 <br />\n<br />\n第一個會被佔領既應該係港台及商台, 因為喺廣播道, 距離駐港步隊既九龍東軍營（原稱「奧士本軍營」) 最近.  之後就係 cctvb 和有線會被佔領 <br />\n<br />\n軍師們要諗吓辦法點樣去保護香港既通訊設施和網絡呀!"},{"pid":"3aa4a7dbd6ccc986e9e78e073ee88b087cf0e80b","tid":1473741,"uid":264724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:12:19.000Z","msg":"求推求推! <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">超簡單 全民集氣方法 一定要谷到 818 全香港支持運動嘅人都識做</span></span><br />\n<br />\n全民係屋企都可以示威:<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Noise-Making&nbsp;定時敲鑊抗爭法</span></span></strong><br />\n自己睇link<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1469010\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1469010</a><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x9LdRkf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx9LdRkf.jpg&h=ac530197&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dh0A4Fp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdh0A4Fp.jpg&h=f71084ad&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ba1c57b02d3680fe0da5f60ca891596ed2113b05","tid":1473741,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4d3731006e5b227406f72408da6a95731894d83","tid":1473741,"uid":115910,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:03:26.000Z","msg":"根本大撚把人真心驚到仆街"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:21:43.000Z","msg":"星期一機場話有TG 又雞飛狗走<br />\n次次發夢一出黑𣄃 啲女又係話走走走"},{"pid":"c883c9bb5b0c356d3e517004411dd7e8937e9bcc","tid":1473741,"uid":167581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:58:43.000Z","msg":"分析好好，推"},{"pid":"dad6611f1ce68442492395d6b5a653338f5d940b","tid":1473741,"uid":167581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1fc07ef9177d319f57e73d0a69c6eb0ff8b47792","tid":1473741,"uid":284932,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:11:52.000Z","msg":"有錯請指教 <br />\n<br />\n深圳步隊來港只需10分鐘, 如果老共真係要出動深圳步隊來香港, 深圳步隊未嚟之前, 我諗佢地先會出動駐港步隊癱瘓香港既通訊設施和網絡, 例如電話打唔到呀, 手機無訊號呀, 上唔到網呀, 睇唔到電視呀, 聽唔到收音機呀, 等等, 以防出動老解的消息和新聞傳出去外國 <br />\n<br />\n第一個會被佔領既應該係港台及商台, 因為喺廣播道, 距離駐港步隊既九龍東軍營（原稱「奧士本軍營」) 最近.  之後就係 cctvb 和有線會被佔領 <br />\n<br />\n軍師們要諗吓辦法點樣去保護香港既通訊設施和網絡呀!"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:03:11.000Z","msg":"有一點要更正，以防出老解消息佢一定唔會防，都防唔到，好多記者會用衛星通訊，除非佢連呢樣都干擾，同埋各領事館都會立即向本國匯報，如果都干擾埋仲大問題，而且有國際法問題，就算係老解唔理都干擾，咁其實全世界都知封港，相信全球各國都會緊急召見中國大使"},{"pid":"c5bfd1fa3ca100023922beb88a78224af5b64b45","tid":1473741,"uid":44646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46b0b17248a97d1abd425ed17244283f358f8103","tid":1473741,"uid":14075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:08:49.000Z","msg":"對內 武警&gt;解放軍"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:20:11.000Z","msg":"問題在於，基本法有規定，特首可要求中央派出駐軍<br />\n駐軍法亦有明確規定用PLA既條文<br />\n技術上呢種情況影響較少(形式上係香港要求)<br />\nPLA如果用來守衛機場、港口，可以令大量警力釋放出來<br />\n個畫面亦唔太衝擊<br />\n對示威者又多多少少有更強阻嚇力<br />\n<br />\n武警在大陸係有另外既法律，而條文不適用於香港<br />\n如果要在香港用武警<br />\n就要由人大表示香港進入緊急狀態<br />\n某些全國法律適用於香港<br />\n此時武警可用，但已經同緊急狀態用PLA一樣係攬炒"},{"pid":"2d75442b0a119e609b8b1f4faafb1d4dbcc7da91","tid":1473741,"uid":117892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:29:36.000Z","msg":"我返屋企瞓都唔使10分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4ef1a05f094a7f68e6b1916bc977c0264d955b2","tid":1473741,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:30:48.000Z","msg":"殺平民攞經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea029cf476326bc963781cc3741608989245ec8a","tid":1473741,"uid":36089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:37:32.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，借一借位~<br />\n<br />\n求求大家，盡快去換美元現鈔！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1429581\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1429581</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5b07c17ff5f2d5da0eebf1e5be16dcf18bef0d4e","tid":1473741,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:59:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">睇下啲有用野啦 <br />\n日日熱門推埋啲無聊野 <br />\n<br />\n依個星期大家應該做好文宣 同 增加知識<br />\n和理非 勇武都係</span>"}]}